\pard\plain \fi720\sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93These are outland pokes, Obo. What does every outland poke want? To a man and woman, they want Hrk destroyed. And you\u8217\'92re a Mazid. You possess the most destructive power known to man. They captured you because they want to use you against your masters. That\u8217\'92s why Ayram was so upset when his girl couldn\u8217\'92t control you.\u8221\'94}
