\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93That is strange, isn't it? I\u8217\'92ve been trying to figure out your role in all of this. These Ayramun aren\u8217\'92t in a position to accommodate a freeloader, so I don\u8217\'92t understand why they would haul you around, or why they brought you back from the dead in the first place.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Probably some old desert superstition,\u8221\'94 Mandri said, thinking back to the old demon witch who\u8217\'92d started this all in the first place.}}